H. Databricks Apps & MCP (Model Context Protocol) — Additional Questions
	22.	What are Databricks Apps (capabilities, supported frameworks, hosting model) and what deployment options are available (UI, CLI, CI/CD)?
References (copy‑paste):

	•	https://docs.databricks.com/aws/en/dev-tools/databricks-apps/
	•	https://docs.databricks.com/aws/en/dev-tools/databricks-apps/get-started
	•	https://docs.databricks.com/aws/en/dev-tools/databricks-apps/deploy
￼

	23.	How do Databricks Apps integrate with platform services (Unity Catalog, Secrets, MLflow, Vector Search / Mosaic AI) and runtime compute (serverless vs cluster-based)?
References (copy‑paste):

	•	https://docs.databricks.com/aws/en/dev-tools/databricks-apps/key-concepts
